short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Helper tools for UW course registration

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A registration tool based on https://github.com/noname01/huskyReg. The original plugin is no longer working. This plugin helps you quickly register for classes that you find on the UW time schedule.
